{"tid":448985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高慧然：香港人不需要支付寶","createTime":"2017-10-26T17:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T15:20:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":513,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"69b35873e5911a8ef4aac624f79c822de7473bfd","tid":448985,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171027/57379154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F57379154&d=fw%2BN0dXYDJQcJJtoF8mp2gHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=81e56034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F57379154&h=2837510c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171027/57379154</a><br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪街巿率先推出支付寶服務，如果幫襯開的顧客以中國新移民為主的話，相信不會遇到太多阻力。微信、支付寶是中國人的社交平台及支付平台，中國人早已經習慣。但是香港人用WhatsApp、facebook進行交流，小面額交易則習慣以八達通代替現金。大家生活在平行時空，我當你無到。<br />\n<br />\n前段時間在香港，逢周末去百佳購物，收銀員見我用匯豐卡，總會提醒我用手機下載某個App，告訴我用手機支付可以收到若干元現金回贈。我當然不予理會。我總覺得，把太多個人資料及銀行資料輸入手機，再交給網絡Apps，是不智的事。中國的Apps就更加不用考慮了，你相信中國人的誠信嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有一部日本電影叫《逃生走佬Family》，作者假設日本突然停電，人們的生活會發生甚麼變化。電子世代，人類太依賴機器，結果一停電就成為世界末日，電子支付全部失效，超巿收銀機無法使用，街頭提款機無法使用，銀行發生擠提。結果，謹小慎微的家庭主婦平時收藏在家中以備不時之需的一筆現金大派用場。都巿人拼命逃離城巿，結果在落後的養豬場，以及小漁村找到新生活，返璞歸真。兜了一大個圈，人們似乎開始明白，高科技雖然方便，但其實並非必需。生活，本來是很簡單的事，是誰讓它變得複雜？<br />\n<br />\n我好像說遠了。我想說，在香港，大額付款用信用卡，小額的可以用八達通，不需要更多的支付方式了。"},{"pid":"6623a97a1e552dfaffb059ef6e4fc3e953605a1a","tid":448985,"uid":61864,"like":91,"dislike":7,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"我始終都係覺得八達通比較方便。"},{"pid":"2a833f6e13feac8e3bbc0bab3558d735c67e5d58","tid":448985,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0cb584542bbf1f00502a37df7059b19004f71e","tid":448985,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2405303002b664da6b594525671bba7003af833","tid":448985,"uid":53687,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"啲point幾個星期前連登仔已經講緊，<br />\n會唔會遲咗啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a946d395be54693e0764e6480310c74a35735f","tid":448985,"uid":22736,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:16:31.000Z","msg":"好似抄連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f500d52c951d11f01fffbd12789ad1b6c68d0665","tid":448985,"uid":44358,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"不過我小額都用ＡＮＤＲＯＩＤ　ＰＡＹ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa69e5fb3ecc8ecec408e5f40d85327d2cb13d4","tid":448985,"uid":47359,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲point幾個星期前連登仔已經講緊，<br />\n會唔會遲咗啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁由佢把口講的確影響多好多人既"},{"pid":"cd4f4a4e43f8b432b1b8f606fe78ad974823dea8","tid":448985,"uid":47359,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"D wade 入左黎未<br />\n<br />\n個人簽名<br />\n----------------------------<br />\nOct 26近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 <br />\n3JR 4法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國 <br />\n5真律師何君堯 6蘇麗珊 7十卜ching<br />\n8D_wade 9RedBaron 10優美開始<br />\n11阿古路 12Romanov 13返六日唔撚易"},{"pid":"f56cdbaa5ffe7bc4d8359396fba194cb4a9bd2a5","tid":448985,"uid":53223,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"買淘寶最方便都係支付寶"},{"pid":"5b950f65bfb073058e57254ed3547158edf4ae59","tid":448985,"uid":22558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"